OL,3,CPoliticians back plans that could give
OL,4,Call prisoners a right to vote
OL,6,FJersey politicians have overwhelmingly
OL,7,Fvoted for a law review which could see
OL,8,Fall prisoners in the island given the
OL,9,Fability to vote.
OL,11,FCurrently, those detained for longer
OL,12,Fthan four years are disqualified from
OL,13,Fhaving their say in an election.
OL,15,FHowever, States members approved the
OL,16,Fprinciples of a proposition which
OL,17,Flisted several other administrative
OL,18,Fchanges and will now be scrutinised by
OL,19,Fa political committee before the plans
OL,20,Freturn to the Assembly for further
OL,21,Fdebate.
